Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:03:02.21,OP_C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1800)\be1}在以刀刃切開吞噬之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:06.82,OP_J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}僕等は目指した　Shangri-La
