Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.32,0:26:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍司 快躲開！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.60,0:26:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.10,0:26:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.50,0:26:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放棄！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.37,0:26:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-劍司！\N-近藤！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.96,0:26:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼穹 - 天空
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.00,0:27:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.90,0:27:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.10,0:27:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.14,0:27:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是「痛楚」
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.24,0:27:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,異界體！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.57,0:27:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.68,0:27:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.21,0:27:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明已經下定決心了…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.48,0:27:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.92,0:27:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.02,0:27:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.26,0:27:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.00,0:27:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,異界體 我就告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.14,0:27:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所教你的戰鬥方法的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.74,0:27:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是消耗戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.34,0:27:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是要忍受痛楚的戰法！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.79,0:28:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是戰鬥的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.69,0:28:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是存在的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.86,0:28:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是面對死亡的恐懼！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.69,0:28:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,異界體！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.20,0:28:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鶴…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.14,0:28:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.50,0:28:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要留在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.57,0:28:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要留在這裡啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.71,0:28:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.68,0:28:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.69,0:28:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.06,0:28:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.27,0:29:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的攻擊出現停滯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.01,0:29:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類軍陸續突破防衛線
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.85,0:29:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前進！別放過這個機會！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.08,0:29:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘可能不斷前進！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.86,0:29:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳 千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.09,0:29:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.73,0:29:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要像是這樣變成這座島就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.24,0:29:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.94,0:29:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會擁抱住你們大家
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.48,0:29:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是媽媽一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.05,0:29:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為此我要和龍宮島合而為一
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.33,0:29:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回歸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.90,0:30:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們回歸虛無吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.84,0:30:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快散開！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.28,0:30:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要感謝自己還活著嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.52,0:30:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是存在於這裡的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.23,0:30:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,異界體…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.78,0:30:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是…C地點…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.48,0:30:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.99,0:30:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見 使用縛狼刃索
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.29,0:30:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.68,0:31:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是能讓人類跟異界體共存的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.82,0:31:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也太多了吧 會超載的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.46,0:31:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 大部分都正傳送到別處
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.59,0:31:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.40,0:31:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍宮島？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.21,0:31:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.61,0:31:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北極傳來資料了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.98,0:31:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞爾維斯的所有伺服器及兀爾德之泉已自動接收
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.12,0:31:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是龐大
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.22,0:31:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠超過之前接收的資料量
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.93,0:32:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎他們已經抵達了紅音的意志跟希望
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.43,0:32:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.73,0:32:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路線淨空
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.07,0:32:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有系統正常
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.00,0:32:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,導航系統正重新接收目標周邊的相關情報
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.74,0:32:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.94,0:32:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁紅音
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.51,0:32:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾經告訴絕望的我們 要我們活下去的人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.53,0:32:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士…就在裡面…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.84,0:32:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.78,0:32:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.22,0:33:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.62,0:33:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有敵人！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.06,0:33:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不會…讓你們進去！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.21,0:33:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始進行核心的再同步作業
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.19,0:33:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.23,0:33:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說過禁止通行了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.93,0:33:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你們搶走的東西還給我們吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.82,0:34:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.82,0:34:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.33,0:34:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…就是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.33,0:34:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.37,0:34:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我…！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.25,0:34:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是敵方星核的騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.52,0:34:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎他…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.49,0:34:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把敵人的意識同化了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.99,0:34:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.36,0:34:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「接受」也是一種力量喔
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.67,0:35:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.44,0:35:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.59,0:35:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.56,0:35:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士 你在那裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.33,0:35:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.20,0:35:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.40,0:35:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.21,0:35:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在吧 就在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.31,0:35:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.61,0:35:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…還在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.71,0:35:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.72,0:35:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.72,0:35:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.86,0:35:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎？你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.93,0:35:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.99,0:36:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為同化的關係 肉體的同化現象復發了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.73,0:36:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.37,0:36:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.87,0:36:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要接受治療一定會康復的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.37,0:36:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.78,0:36:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到島上吧 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.25,0:36:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.88,0:36:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星核…開始行動了！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.02,0:36:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是現在 發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.89,0:37:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正前方出現敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.84,0:37:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.17,0:37:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後的同化開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.65,0:37:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-怎麼會這樣…\N-乙姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.36,0:37:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.70,0:37:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的星核正想和天空連繫
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.34,0:37:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它想要和大氣層外的異界體一起覆蓋住整個地球
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.74,0:37:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.08,0:37:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同化Mark VII武器攻擊它！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.71,0:37:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.08,0:37:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扳機由真矢來按
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.88,0:37:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.40,0:38:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將Mark Zein的能量用最大的功率釋放出去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.73,0:38:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機會只有一次而已
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.24,0:38:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多的話一騎的身體無法負荷
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.41,0:38:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對它們來說 那或許是唯一的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.25,0:38:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此 也不是最後的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.65,0:38:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.94,0:38:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個星核也跟我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.44,0:39:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了闡述生與死、存在與虛無是表裡合一不斷延續的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.41,0:39:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才會誕生在這個世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.65,0:39:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬 妳回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.55,0:39:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到另一個星核的身邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.89,0:39:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.90,0:39:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,異界體…全都往下掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.80,0:39:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溝口先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.57,0:39:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認法夫那部隊所有駕駛員平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.27,0:39:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辦到了 他們辦到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.29,0:39:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地底…起風了？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.86,0:39:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核心和島合而為一了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.16,0:39:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風…？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.60,0:39:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在這裡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.45,0:40:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.35,0:40:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就可以回去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.85,0:40:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.39,0:40:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mark Nicht！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.26,0:40:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.46,0:40:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星核用自己的死亡賦予異界體成為了個體
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.20,0:40:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再這樣下去會拖累所有的人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.23,0:40:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.40,0:40:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.84,0:40:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.11,0:40:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來 遠見！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.71,0:40:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也…一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.25,0:40:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.38,0:40:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎！一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.89,0:40:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜下來！同步直接連結還沒中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.56,0:40:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要少了任何一人 同步連結就沒有作用
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.23,0:40:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是妳在戰鬥之前告訴我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.53,0:41:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎…他還活著…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.91,0:41:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不存在於任何地方 存在於這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.55,0:41:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在與虛無正相互對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.89,0:41:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不存在於任何地方…存在於這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.79,0:41:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎…總士…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.30,0:41:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是將一切回歸虛無 來自異界體的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.67,0:41:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕在現實的世界中 我們的存在已經消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.21,0:41:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.25,0:41:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.25,0:41:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們…還在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.35,0:41:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.95,0:41:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.90,0:42:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲洋！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.01,0:42:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.23,0:42:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.40,0:42:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人類的宇宙艦隊以及大氣層外的異界體核心
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.71,0:42:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雙方都燃燒殆盡而墜落了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.01,0:42:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.78,0:42:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整艘艦艇在出發之前就被摧毀
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.61,0:42:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是引擎仍然毫髮無傷
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.78,0:43:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將機體的構造同化 把控制權交由系統管理
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.09,0:43:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起飛之後就由我來操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.33,0:43:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能飛嗎 一騎？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.20,0:43:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然能飛
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.86,0:43:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有我陪著你…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.23,0:43:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.97,0:43:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.77,0:43:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星核理解生命的循環了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.01,0:43:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是乙姬嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.81,0:43:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 她本人是不可能再生的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.95,0:43:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那將只是複製出同樣的事物 違背了生命的本質
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.09,0:43:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾經是乙姬的存在轉生成為新的事物了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.03,0:43:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼她終將成長為核心 並且能夠與我們對話的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.07,0:43:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我們把這座島當作希望
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.67,0:43:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且繼續留在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.31,0:44:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續直走就能回到島上了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.38,0:44:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到頭來還是你救了我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.75,0:44:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎 我教導異界體什麼是痛楚與存在
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.76,0:44:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我也理解了他們的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.93,0:44:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理解了存在與虛無的循環
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.93,0:44:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在與虛無的循環？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.34,0:44:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.67,0:44:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.04,0:44:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經幾乎不存在了 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.88,0:44:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到島上一起接受治療吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.18,0:44:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此一來一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.55,0:44:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就這麼做吧 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.12,0:44:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上就要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.72,0:44:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士 你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.06,0:44:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別再說了 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.73,0:44:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會到異界體那裡一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.30,0:44:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後再度創造出自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.90,0:45:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不知道會花上多久
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.74,0:45:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.88,0:45:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士 你在吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.61,0:45:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那裡吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.32,0:45:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士…總士！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.89,0:45:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.49,0:45:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我們重逢為止…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.44,0:45:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.45,0:45:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mark VII的緊急修理完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.85,0:45:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時都可以出動
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.26,0:45:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.39,0:45:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員的精神狀態也穩定了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.66,0:45:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.73,0:46:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打開第七巨龍之洞
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.20,0:46:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法夫那Mark VII 出動！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.98,0:46:22.97,OP_C,NTP,0,0,5,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}我可以懵懂無知吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.98,0:46:22.97,OP_J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}愚かでいいのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.05,0:46:27.38,OP_C,NTP,0,0,5,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}眺望著夢想的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.05,0:46:27.38,OP_J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}見渡す夢の痕
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.52,0:46:37.43,OP_C,NTP,0,0,5,,{\fad(300,3000)\fs20\be1}再見了 湛藍的歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.52,0:46:37.43,OP_J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,3000)\an9\fs18\be1}さよなら　蒼き日々よ
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.81,0:46:55.84,OP_C,NTP,0,0,5,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}即使將珍貴的事物當成跳板
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.81,0:46:55.84,OP_J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}大切な何かを　踏み台にしてまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.88,0:47:01.94,OP_C,NTP,0,0,5,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}也想摘下最高處的蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.88,0:47:01.94,OP_J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}一番高い林檎　掴みたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.05,0:47:08.05,OP_C,NTP,0,0,5,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}失去了才察覺到值得尊崇的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.05,0:47:08.05,OP_J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}無くしてから気付く　尊いモノ
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.13,0:47:15.46,OP_C,NTP,0,0,5,,{\fad(300,1800)\fs20\be1}年幼的我們總是不得要領
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.13,0:47:15.46,OP_J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1800)\an9\fs18\be1}幼い僕等は　的はずれだらけさ
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.67,0:47:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士 我就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.01,0:47:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在這裡等你
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.13,0:47:20.07,OP_C,NTP,0,0,5,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}充盈於每一天的鎮壓
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.13,0:47:20.07,OP_J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}満ち足りた日々の制圧は
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.01,0:47:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.17,0:47:23.26,OP_C,NTP,0,0,5,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}使得情緒變得不安定
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.17,0:47:23.26,OP_J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}情緒不安定になる
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.34,0:47:29.34,OP_C,NTP,0,0,5,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}即使受傷也祈禱能拍動羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.34,0:47:29.34,OP_J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}傷を負ってでも　羽ばたきたいと願うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.48,0:47:35.81,OP_C,NTP,0,0,5,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}我可以懵懂無知吧 眺望著夢想的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.48,0:47:35.81,OP_J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}愚かでいいのだろう　見渡す夢の痕
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.89,0:47:41.79,OP_C,NTP,0,0,5,,{\fad(300,1000)\fs20\be1}再見了 湛藍的歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.89,0:47:41.79,OP_J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)\an9\fs18\be1}さよなら　蒼き日々よ
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.07,0:47:53.98,OP_C,NTP,0,0,5,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}正因為保持距離 才能得知自由的份量
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.07,0:47:53.98,OP_J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}距離をおいてこそ　自分の大きさを知る
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.08,0:48:00.35,OP_C,NTP,0,0,5,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}未成熟的心甚至無法理解這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.08,0:48:00.35,OP_J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}未熟な心は　それさえ分からないまま
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.49,0:48:06.58,OP_C,NTP,0,0,5,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}現在就敢如此斷言吧 這裡就是所謂的樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.49,0:48:06.58,OP_J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}今なら言えるだろう　此処がそう楽園さ
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.72,0:48:12.22,OP_C,NTP,0,0,5,,{\fad(300,1300)\fs20\be1}再見了 湛藍的歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.72,0:48:12.22,OP_J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1300)\an9\fs18\be1}さよなら　蒼き日々よ
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.13,0:48:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我就能理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.80,0:48:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是充滿痛苦的人生 我還是會選擇存在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.61,0:48:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了能夠再度見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.35,0:48:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.78,0:48:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天我一定會回去
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.15,0:48:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到有你在的地方…
